data.description: Awesome remodel in the heart of Murray. Location! Location! This condo has been updated from top to bottom. New carpet, two tone paint, windows, pella sliding glass door, stainless steel appliances including gas range and refrigerator, granite tops. New base, case  trim and door hardware. Even the smoke detectors, CO detector and doorbell are new. The unit has one parking space in garage and one other assigned space. A fireplace and deck add to the enjoyment. The complex has plenty of amenities including pool, clubhouse and common area. Unit truly is ready to move in and enjoy. Will Not Disappoint!! *Buyer to verify all info.
